-- Ghana Cocoa Board to Sign $1.5 Billion Trade Finance Agreement on Sept. 22
-- Moses Mozart Dzawu
-- 2010-09-20T13:03:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/ghana-cocoa-board-to-sign-1-5-billion-trade-finance-agreement-on-sept-22.html

          
          
             The Ghana Cocoa Board plans to sign
a $1.5 billion trade finance agreement with 12 banks on Sept. 22
in the capital, Accra, Yaw Adu-Ampomah, deputy chief executive
officer, said by phone today from the city.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
 mdzawu@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        